<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fa" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>اطلاعات اشتراک - <%= data.email %></title>
    
    <!-- Google Fonts: Vazirmatn & Roboto -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&family=Vazirmatn:wght@400;500;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/rastikerdar/vazirmatn@v33.0.0/Vazirmatn-font-face.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/qrcodejs/1.0.0/qrcode.min.js"></script>
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0d1117;
            --card-bg: rgba(22, 27, 34, 0.7);
            --card-border: rgba(48, 54, 61, 0.8);
            --text-primary: #e6edf3;
            --text-secondary: #8b949e;
            --accent-blue: #2f81f7;
            --accent-blue-hover: #388bfd;
            --accent-green: #3fb950;
            --accent-red: #f85149;
            --font-fa: 'Vazirmatn', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            --font-en: 'Roboto', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            --radius-xl: 24px;
            --radius-lg: 16px;
            --radius-md: 12px;
            --radius-sm: 8px;
            --shadow-card: 0 12px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            --shadow-glow: 0 0 20px rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.15);
            --transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-family: var(--font-fa);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 15% 50%, rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.08), transparent 25%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 85% 30%, rgba(63, 185, 80, 0.05), transparent 25%);
            background-attachment: fixed;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 520px;
            padding: 24px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .glass-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
            padding: 36px 32px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-card), var(--shadow-glow);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            animation: fadeInScale 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: scale(0.96) translateY(10px);
        }

        @keyframes fadeInScale {
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1) translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .avatar {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2f81f7 0%, #8957e5 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.25);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-family: var(--font-en);
            border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin: 0;
            color: #ffffff;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
            font-family: var(--font-en);
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .status-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 16px;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }

        .status-active {
            background-color: rgba(46, 160, 67, 0.15);
            color: var(--accent-green);
            border-color: rgba(46, 160, 67, 0.4);
        }

        .status-inactive {
            background-color: rgba(248, 81, 73, 0.15);
            color: var(--accent-red);
            border-color: rgba(248, 81, 73, 0.4);
        }

        .status-badge::before {
            content: "";
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-left: 8px;
        }

        .status-active::before {
            background-color: var(--accent-green);
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--accent-green);
        }

        .status-inactive::before {
            background-color: var(--accent-red);
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--accent-red);
        }

        .copy-section {
            background-color: rgba(1, 4, 9, 0.6);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: 6px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            position: relative;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .copy-section:hover, .copy-section:focus-within {
            border-color: rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.6);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.2);
        }

        .copy-input {
            background: transparent;
            border: none;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-family: var(--font-en);
            font-size: 14px;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            flex-grow: 1;
            outline: none;
            direction: ltr;
            text-align: left;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .copy-input::selection {
            background: rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.3);
        }

        .copy-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(48, 54, 61, 1), rgba(33, 38, 45, 1));
            color: var(--text-primary);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-family: var(--font-fa);
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            white-space: nowrap;
            margin-left: 4px;
            box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .copy-btn svg {
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            fill: currentColor;
        }

        .copy-btn:hover {
            background: var(--text-primary);
            color: var(--bg-color);
            border-color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .copy-btn:active {
            transform: scale(0.96);
        }

        .grid-stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .stat-card {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: var(--transition);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .stat-card::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.1), transparent);
        }

        .stat-card:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
            border-color: rgba(139, 148, 158, 0.4);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .stat-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            margin: 0 auto 12px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .stat-card:nth-child(1) .stat-icon {
            background-color: rgba(137, 87, 229, 0.15);
            color: #d2a8ff;
        }
        
        .stat-card:nth-child(2) .stat-icon {
            background-color: rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.15);
            color: #79c0ff;
        }

        .stat-icon svg {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            fill: currentColor;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .stat-value {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-family: var(--font-en);
            display: flex;
            align-items: baseline;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 4px;
        }

        .stat-unit {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-family: var(--font-fa);
        }

        .progress-container {
            width: 100%;
            height: 6px;
            background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            border-radius: 99px;
            margin-top: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        .progress-bar {
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 99px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2f81f7, #79c0ff);
            transition: width 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
            width: 0%;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.5);
        }
        
        .progress-bar.danger {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #da3633, #ff7b72);
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(218, 54, 51, 0.5);
        }

        .action-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .btn-link {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 14px 24px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: var(--transition);
            flex: 1;
            gap: 10px;
            box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }

        .btn-link svg {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            fill: currentColor;
        }

        .btn-telegram {
            background-color: rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.12);
            color: #58a6ff;
            border: 1px solid rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-telegram:hover {
            background-color: rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.25);
            border-color: rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.6);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn-whatsapp {
            background-color: rgba(46, 160, 67, 0.12);
            color: #56d364;
            border: 1px solid rgba(46, 160, 67, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-whatsapp:hover {
            background-color: rgba(46, 160, 67, 0.25);
            border-color: rgba(46, 160, 67, 0.6);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .toast {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 32px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(100px);
            background-color: var(--accent-green);
            color: #000000;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(63, 185, 80, 0.4);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
            z-index: 1000;
            pointer-events: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .toast svg {
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
            fill: currentColor;
        }

        .toast.show {
            transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .import-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .import-col {
            flex: 1;
            position: relative;
        }

        .btn-import {
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 14px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            font-family: var(--font-fa);
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
        }

        .btn-import:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            border-color: rgba(139, 148, 158, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-android { color: #3ddc84; }
        .btn-ios { color: #ffffff; }

        .dropdown-menu {
            position: absolute;
            top: 100%;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            margin-top: 8px;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 16px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            transition: var(--transition);
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .dropdown-menu.show {
            opacity: 1;
            visibility: visible;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .dropdown-item {
            display: block;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: var(--font-en);
            font-size: 14px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            transition: var(--transition);
            text-align: left;
            direction: ltr;
        }

        .dropdown-item:hover {
            background: rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.15);
            color: #79c0ff;
        }

        .configs-section {
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .configs-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0 0 16px 0;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .configs-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
            max-height: 240px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding-left: 4px;
            padding-right: 8px;
        }

        .configs-list::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
        .configs-list::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border-radius: 4px; }
        .configs-list::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius: 4px; }
        .configs-list::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }

        .config-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            padding: 12px 16px;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .config-item:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }

        .config-info {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .config-badge {
            background: rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.15);
            color: #79c0ff;
            font-family: var(--font-en);
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .config-name {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
        }

        .btn-copy-sm {
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            font-family: var(--font-fa);
            font-size: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            margin-right: 12px;
        }

        .btn-copy-sm:hover {
            background: var(--text-primary);
            color: var(--bg-color);
            border-color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .glass-card {
                padding: 28px 20px;
            }
            .grid-stats {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .import-buttons, .action-links {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }

        .announcements-container {
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .alert {
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            animation: slideDown 0.4s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes slideDown {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .alert svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; fill: currentColor; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .alert-info { background: rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.25); color: #c9e1ff; border-color: rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.5); }
        .alert-warning { background: rgba(210, 153, 34, 0.25); color: #f2cc79; border-color: rgba(210, 153, 34, 0.5); }
        .alert-danger { background: rgba(248, 81, 73, 0.25); color: #ffb1af; border-color: rgba(248, 81, 73, 0.5); }
        .alert-success { background: rgba(46, 160, 67, 0.25); color: #7ee787; border-color: rgba(46, 160, 67, 0.5); }

        .alert-content {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            width: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .alert-text-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .alert-date {
            font-size: 11px;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            padding: 3px 8px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            white-space: nowrap;
            font-family: var(--font-en);
        }

        .alert-msg {
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .btn-more {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-family: var(--font-fa);
            cursor: pointer;
            white-space: nowrap;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .btn-more:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
        }

        .modal-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            z-index: 2000;
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .modal-overlay.show {
            opacity: 1;
            visibility: visible;
        }

        .modal-content {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            padding: 32px;
            text-align: center;
            transform: scale(0.9);
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            max-width: 90%;
            width: 320px;
        }

        .modal-overlay.show .modal-content {
            transform: scale(1);
        }

        .qr-container {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .modal-close {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 24px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            font-family: var(--font-fa);
            font-size: 14px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            width: 100%;
        }

        .modal-close:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
        }

        .btn-qr {
            background: transparent;
            border: none;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            padding: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            border-radius: 4px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .btn-qr:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .btn-qr svg {
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
            fill: currentColor;
        }

        .config-actions {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <% if (data.ANNOUNCEMENTS && data.ANNOUNCEMENTS.length > 0) { %>
        <div class="announcements-container">
            <% data.ANNOUNCEMENTS.forEach(ann => { 
                let iconPath = "M11 15h2v2h-2v-2zm0-8h2v6h-2V7zm.99-5C6.47 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.47 10 9.99 10C17.52 22 22 17.52 22 12S17.52 2 11.99 2zM12 20c-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8-3.58 8-8 8z";
                if (ann.type === 'danger') iconPath = "M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 15h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2V7h2v6z";
                if (ann.type === 'success') iconPath = "M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z";
            %>
            <div class="alert alert-<%= ann.type %>">
                <div class="alert-content">
                    <div class="alert-text-wrapper">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="<%= iconPath %>"/></svg>
                        <% if (ann.date) { %>
                            <span class="alert-date"><%= ann.date %></span>
                        <% } %>
                        <span class="alert-msg"><%= ann.message %></span>
                    </div>
                    <button class="btn-more" onclick="showAnnouncement('<%= ann.type %>', '<%= ann.date || '' %>', '<%= ann.message.replace(/'/g, "\\'") %>')">بیشتر...</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <% }); %>
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <div class="glass-card">
            <div class="header">
                <div class="avatar"><%= data.email.substring(0, 2) %></div>
                <h1 class="title"><%= data.email %></h1>
                <div class="subtitle">پنل کاربری اشتراک شما</div>
                
                <% if (data.enable) { %>
                    <div class="status-badge status-active">وضعیت: فعال</div>
                <% } else { %>
                    <div class="status-badge status-inactive">وضعیت: غیرفعال</div>
                <% } %>
            </div>

            <div class="copy-section">
                <input type="text" id="subUrl" class="copy-input" value="<%= data.suburl %>" readonly>
                <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyUrl()">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M16 1H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14h2V3h12V1zm3 4H8c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h11c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V7c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 16H8V7h11v14z"/></svg>
                    کپی لینک
                </button>
            </div>

            <%
                const totalGB = (data.total / 1073741824).toFixed(2);
                const usedGB = ((data.up + data.down) / 1073741824).toFixed(2);
                const percentUsed = data.total > 0 ? Math.min(100, Math.round(((data.up + data.down) / data.total) * 100)) : 0;
                const isDanger = percentUsed > 85;
                
                let remainingDays = "نامشخص";
                let remainingDaysVal = -1;
                try {
                    const expiry = parseInt(data.expiryTime, 10);
                    if (expiry === 0) {
                        remainingDays = "بدون انقضا";
                    } else if (expiry > Date.now()) {
                        remainingDaysVal = Math.floor((expiry - Date.now()) / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24));
                        remainingDays = remainingDaysVal + " روز";
                    } else {
                        remainingDays = "منقضی شده";
                    }
                } catch(e) {}
            %>

            <div class="grid-stats">
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-icon">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 4h-1V2h-2v2H8V2H6v2H5c-1.11 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L3 20a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 16H5V10h14v10zm0-12H5V6h14v2zm-7 5h5v5h-5z"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-label">زمان باقیمانده</div>
                    <div class="stat-value">
                        <% if (remainingDaysVal >= 0) { %>
                            <%= remainingDaysVal %> <span class="stat-unit">روز</span>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: var(--font-fa);"><%= remainingDays %></span>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-icon">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M13 2.05v3.03c3.39.49 6 3.39 6 6.92 0 .9-.22 1.76-.61 2.53l2.5 2.5c1.33-1.42 2.11-3.32 2.11-5.03 0-4.97-4.03-9-9-9zM12 19c-3.87 0-7-3.13-7-7 0-3.53 2.61-6.43 6-6.92V2.05c-5.06.5-9 4.76-9 9.95 0 5.52 4.47 10 9.99 10 3.31 0 6.24-1.61 8.06-4.09l-2.6-2.6C16.17 17.17 14.22 19 12 19z"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-label">ترافیک مصرف شده</div>
                    <div class="stat-value">
                        <%= usedGB %> <span class="stat-unit">/ <%= data.total === 0 ? '∞' : totalGB %> GB</span>
                    </div>
                    <% if (data.total > 0) { %>
                        <div class="progress-container">
                            <div class="progress-bar <%= isDanger ? 'danger' : '' %>" style="width: 0%" data-target="<%= percentUsed %>%"></div>
                        </div>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="import-buttons">
                <div class="import-col">
                    <button class="btn-import" onclick="toggleDropdown('android-menu')">
                        <svg class="btn-android" viewBox="64 64 896 896" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M448.3 225.2c-18.6 0-32 13.4-32 31.9s13.5 31.9 32 31.9c18.6 0 32-13.4 32-31.9.1-18.4-13.4-31.9-32-31.9zm393.9 96.4c-13.8-13.8-32.7-21.5-53.2-21.5-3.9 0-7.4.4-10.7 1v-1h-3.6c-5.5-30.6-18.6-60.5-38.1-87.4-18.7-25.7-43-47.9-70.8-64.9l25.1-35.8v-3.3c0-.8.4-2.3.7-3.8.6-2.4 1.4-5.5 1.4-8.9 0-18.5-13.5-31.9-32-31.9-9.8 0-19.5 5.7-25.9 15.4l-29.3 42.1c-30-9.8-62.4-15-93.8-15-31.3 0-63.7 5.2-93.8 15L389 79.4c-6.6-9.6-16.1-15.4-26-15.4-18.6 0-32 13.4-32 31.9 0 6.2 2.5 12.8 6.7 17.4l22.6 32.3c-28.7 17-53.5 39.4-72.2 65.1-19.4 26.9-32 56.8-36.7 87.4h-5.5v1c-3.2-.6-6.7-1-10.7-1-20.3 0-39.2 7.5-53.1 21.3-13.8 13.8-21.5 32.6-21.5 53v235c0 20.3 7.5 39.1 21.4 52.9 13.8 13.8 32.8 21.5 53.2 21.5 3.9 0 7.4-.4 10.7-1v93.5c0 29.2 23.9 53.1 53.2 53.1H331v58.3c0 20.3 7.5 39.1 21.4 52.9 13.8 13.8 32.8 21.5 53.2 21.5 20.3 0 39.2-7.5 53.1-21.3 13.8-13.8 21.5-32.6 21.5-53v-58.2H544v58.1c0 20.3 7.5 39.1 21.4 52.9 13.8 13.8 32.8 21.5 53.2 21.5 20.4 0 39.2-7.5 53.1-21.6 13.8-13.8 21.5-32.6 21.5-53v-58.2h31.9c29.3 0 53.2-23.8 53.2-53.1v-91.4c3.2.6 6.7 1 10.7 1 20.3 0 39.2-7.5 53.1-21.3 13.8-13.8 21.5-32.6 21.5-53v-235c-.1-20.3-7.6-39-21.4-52.9zM246 609.6c0 6.8-3.9 10.6-10.7 10.6-6.8 0-10.7-3.8-10.7-10.6V374.5c0-6.8 3.9-10.6 10.7-10.6 6.8 0 10.7 3.8 10.7 10.6v235.1zm131.1-396.8c37.5-27.3 85.3-42.3 135-42.3s97.5 15.1 135 42.5c32.4 23.7 54.2 54.2 62.7 87.5H314.4c8.5-33.4 30.5-64 62.7-87.7zm39.3 674.7c-.6 5.6-4.4 8.7-10.5 8.7-6.8 0-10.7-3.8-10.7-10.6v-58.2h21.2v60.1zm202.3 8.7c-6.8 0-10.7-3.8-10.7-10.6v-58.2h21.2v60.1c-.6 5.6-4.3 8.7-10.5 8.7zm95.8-132.6H309.9V364h404.6v399.6zm85.2-154c0 6.8-3.9 10.6-10.7 10.6-6.8 0-10.7-3.8-10.7-10.6V374.5c0-6.8 3.9-10.6 10.7-10.6 6.8 0 10.7 3.8 10.7 10.6v235.1zM576.1 225.2c-18.6 0-32 13.4-32 31.9s13.5 31.9 32 31.9c18.6 0 32.1-13.4 32.1-32-.1-18.6-13.4-31.8-32.1-31.8z"></path></svg>
                        واردسازی Android
                        <svg viewBox="64 64 896 896" width="12" height="12" fill="currentColor"><path d="M884 256h-75c-5.1 0-9.9 2.5-12.9 6.6L512 654.2 227.9 262.6c-3-4.1-7.8-6.6-12.9-6.6h-75c-6.5 0-10.3 7.4-6.5 12.7l352.6 486.1c12.8 17.6 39 17.6 51.7 0l352.6-486.1c3.9-5.3.1-12.7-6.4-12.7z"></path></svg>
                    </button>
                    <div id="android-menu" class="dropdown-menu">
                        <a href="v2rayng://install-sub?url=<%= encodeURIComponent(data.suburl) %>&name=<%= encodeURIComponent(data.email) %>" class="dropdown-item">v2rayNG</a>
                        <a href="nekobox://import-sub?url=<%= encodeURIComponent(data.suburl) %>&name=<%= encodeURIComponent(data.email) %>" class="dropdown-item">NekoBox / MahsaNG</a>
                        <a href="clash://install-config?url=<%= encodeURIComponent(data.suburl) %>&name=<%= encodeURIComponent(data.email) %>" class="dropdown-item">Clash for Android</a>
